Bobby Dunn https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bobby_Dunn 0 Bobby Dunn (28 August 1890 – 24 March 1937) was a comic actor who appeared in several Laurel and Hardy comedies, including Tit for Tat. Also appeared in Duck Soup with The Marx Brothers.. He was one of the original Keystone Kops in Hoffmeyer's Legacy.
